```
Help on CONTROLLER in module __main__ object:

class CONTROLLER(builtins.object)
 |  this **class** is the module to control the input, output and cuda in SPONGE
 |
 |  Methods defined here:
 |
 |  Command(self, arg1, arg2=None)
